init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Wasn't he buried in Arlington cemetery?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: His wiki page tells you that yes, he is dead.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Half of the results tell you that he is dead, and half tell you to look at more results.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So you google his wiki page again, to make sure that the first half was right.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the wiki page is gone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You go to a different site.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They've taken down all of JFK's pages.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look at the page source.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: You look at the page source.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You ask "How did you get my mother's number?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and the voice replies "I know where you live, Barack," in a tone that says "this is not up for discussion."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So you go to your parent's house.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You walk in to see your mother cooking dinner and JFK sitting at the table.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He has a single piece of paper in front of him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He looks up at you and smiles.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We need to talk about your next move."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I go golfing every day and eat organic cuisine."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "That's not the real you," says JFK.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: JFK looks at him, then turns to the paper.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He stares at it, and then looks up.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And Obama leaves the house, and goes to play golf.
